com.mewna.catnip.cache.view

Interface NamedCacheView<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of the entity held by this cache.
    All Superinterfaces:
    CacheView<T>, Iterable<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MutableNamedCacheView<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompositeNamedCacheView, DefaultNamedCacheView, EmptyCacheView, EmptyNamedCacheView, NoopCacheView

    public interface NamedCacheView<T>
extends CacheView<T>
    A CacheView that provides utilities for finding elements based on their name.
    Since:
    12/15/18
    Author:
    natanbc
